OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fand patchy rain start clearing western
OL,7,FScotland on Wednesday. Then generally
OL,8,Ffine and dry with light winds and
OL,9,Fplenty of sunny spells. Very warm,
OL,10,Fstaying hot in the south.
